{"tid":1277982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《7.1發夢賽後檢討》","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:03:20.000Z","uid":94771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b80c179a3c579dfa48c9554d6a243745bbc1e19b","tid":1277982,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"大家認為7.1有咩得失? 請大家理性發表意見<br />\n<br />\n列明好處，壞處<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n<br />\n運動士氣變大<br />\n再次引起國際關注<br />\n和理非不認同 但 同時會了理解 不責罵<br />\n泛民民陣不割席<br />\n將問題重心放返係政府<br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n<br />\n民意反轉? 《待手足去證實》<br />\n比子彈對家 （對家有新材料）<br />\n建制派選情變好<br />\n有手足面臨嚴重的法律責任"},{"pid":"b9dc2b13935bf45981100b8c97716a3a8741098a","tid":1277982,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67941fa24847724fed432d400846a26b201b508","tid":1277982,"uid":71447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:41:51.000Z","msg":"好:<br />\n尋晚有人有宣言好似加多一樣訴求<br />\n解散立法會 要求真普選<br />\n呢個非常好<br />\n<br />\n壞:<br />\n無做出妥協<br />\n個人認為最好都係陳方安生個建議<br />\n1 撤回條例<br />\n2 特赦兩邊<br />\n3 獨立調查血色六月<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個時侯絕對要重申整理一下訴求<br />\n宣言整理好 言論一致<br />\n以後文宣工作更容易做<br />\n更容易打入民心<br />\n更容易爭取中間派"},{"pid":"6bf69e8d35af87b64121a6ec941416221a0f366a","tid":1277982,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e9a9f4af8db24ee055ece15de66e7f1655dd2b","tid":1277982,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae84448e20efab0eb8c6ff84059bafd605c94677","tid":1277982,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:52:59.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好搞道歉<br />\n唔好搞記招"},{"pid":"31f727a9c262f855c0d712066f9d9470f2625015","